SIMPLE: unapt
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unapt
<hw>Un*apt"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Inapt;
slow; dull.</def> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Unsuitable; unfit; inappropriate.</def>
<rj><au>Macaulay.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Not accustomed and not likely; not
disposed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I am a soldier and <qex>unapt</qex> to weep.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un*apt"ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un*apt"ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unaquit</ent>⟦br⟧
